sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend (React / UI Components)
    participant BE as Backend Controller (Express.js)
    participant DB as MongoDB Atlas Database
    participant Gemini as External LLM (Google Gemini)
    participant Cloud as Cloudinary (Image Storage)

    Note over User, DB: 1. User Authentication & Property Management (CRUD)
    rect rgb(240, 245, 255)
        User->>FE: Click Register/Login
        FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/register or /login
        BE->>DB: Check/Save User Credentials (bcrypt)
        DB-->>BE: User Document
        BE-->>FE: Return JSON Web Token (JWT) + User Profile
        
        Note over User, Cloud: Authorized Listing Creation
        User->>FE: Fill Listing Form (Add Title, Price, Location, Image File)
        FE->>Cloud: Upload Image File directly/via Multer
        Cloud-->>FE: Return Secure Image URL
        FE->>BE: POST /api/properties (Include Image URL + JWT)
        BE->>DB: Save Property/Land Schema (Linked with User ObjectId)
        DB-->>BE: Success Status
        BE-->>FE: Redirect to Dashboard / Show Toast Success
    end

    Note over User, Gemini: 2. Property Discovery & Search Modules
    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        alt Traditional Search
            User->>FE: Input static filters (Location, Property Type, Budget)
            FE->>BE: GET /api/properties?location=...&price=...
            BE->>DB: Run MongoDB Queries (Exact match)
            DB-->>BE: Return Listing Documents
            BE-->>FE: Render Property Grid
        else AI Chatbot Search
            User->>FE: Type Natural Language (e.g., "2BHK rent under 40k in OMR")
            FE->>BE: POST /api/ai/search { query }
            BE->>BE: Execute parseQueryHeuristic(query)
            alt Gemini API Active
                BE->>Gemini: Parse query text to structured JSON filters
                Gemini-->>BE: Return Filter JSON (type, price range, bedrooms, etc.)
            end
            BE->>DB: Run MongoDB Query (Apply progressive relaxation if no results)
            DB-->>BE: Return Listing Documents
            alt Gemini API Active
                BE->>Gemini: Request one-sentence summary of listings
                Gemini-->>BE: Return conversational summary text
            end
            BE-->>FE: Return { filters, results, summary, relaxed }
            FE-->>User: Render Message Bubble + Parameter Chips + Result Cards
        end
    end

    Note over User, DB: 3. Detail View, Comparison, and Contact
    rect rgb(240, 255, 245)
        User->>FE: Select multiple properties for Comparison
        FE->>BE: POST /api/ai/compare { properties }
        alt Gemini API Active
            BE->>Gemini: Analyze properties (trade-offs, value-for-money, area)
            Gemini-->>BE: Return AI Comparative Summary
        else Fallback
            BE->>BE: Run fallback comparison logic (rules engine)
        end
        BE-->>FE: Return comparison summary + tag matrix
        FE-->>User: Render Comparison Modal

        Note over User, BE: Lead Generation / Contact Owner
        User->>FE: Click "Call Agent" or "Send Message"
        FE->>BE: Get Owner Profile details (populate owner ObjectId)
        BE->>DB: Query User schema by Owner ID (fetch phone, email)
        DB-->>BE: Owner Contact Info
        BE-->>FE: Display verified "Click-to-Call" (tel:...) link or WhatsApp widget
    end
